  <chapter>
    <title id="s.2">Installation</title>

    <sect1>
      <title id="s.2.1">Installation on Linux</title>

      <para>Execute the following command as root<programlisting>rpm -i eolfix-x.x.x-1.i386.rpm</programlisting></para>

      <para>where x.x.x indicates package version.</para>

      <para>You can use <ulink
      url="http://fr2.rpmfind.net/linux/rpm2html/search.php?query=eolfix&amp;system=&amp;arch=">http://rpmfind.net</ulink>
      to search for RPM appropriate for your distribution.</para>
    </sect1>

