    <sect1>
      <title>Installation on Windows</title>

      <para>Unzip the file eolfix-x.x.x-win32.zip to some directory. To
      take advantage of UNIX shell scripting you might want to run eolfix
      from Cygwin. Consider installing <ulink
      url="http://www.cygwin.com/">Cygwin</ulink> on your Windows
      machine.</para>
    </sect1>
